878
01:22:46.475 --> 01:22:49.783
Damn it. if you're old. just die. Why are you trying so hard to live?

879
01:22:53.473 --> 01:22:54.783
Excuse me. Chief Son.

880
01:22:55.391 --> 01:22:59.514
