892
01:24:11.808 --> 01:24:12.949
Eat a lot.

893
01:24:12.950 --> 01:24:14.408
Oh. grandma.

894
01:24:37.475 --> 01:24:38.740
Let's finish quickly and go.

895
01:24:38.741 --> 01:24:40.140
Hey. hey. stop.

896
01:24:40.141 --> 01:24:42.157
Hey. stop! Hey. block him!

