1004
01:33:32.283 --> 01:33:35.491
Hae-ni! Hae-ni!

1005
01:33:50.058 --> 01:33:51.158
Go.

1006
01:33:59.266 --> 01:34:00.241
Gotcha.

1007
01:34:03.933 --> 01:34:06.450
