1035
01:35:52.682 --> 01:35:54.324
Because it was the right thing to do.

1036
01:36:39.141 --> 01:36:40.616
Why aren't you going?

1037
01:36:42.141 --> 01:36:43.658
Goodbye.

1038
01:37:20.200 --> 01:37:22.992
Mu-yong. do you remember what I said?

1039
